<br>
<br>
this period between 1am and 10am is for respawn <br>
<br>
POACHING the planes is anyone going in during this respawn period and killing mobs for whatever reason.<br>
<br>
This happened to the PoG open raid yesterday on the 15th.<br>
there were 4 mobs on the west side of the river not including the whorl of natural energy and none of the mobs repoped during the 8 hours we were present.<br>
<br>
I talked to Mystala and Jiffybag of heroes who had the plane booked the evening before the finished at 1am EST<br>
<br>
at 2pm EST assuming a 13 hour respawn adn not an 8 hour there were still no repops and there were none the entire time we were there which was until 6pm EST which one can at that point state that a group or groups were in PoG between 6am and 9am EST killing the west side mobs.<br>
<br>
THIS IS POACHING and defeats the purpose of the calandar system.  shall we have all planes go FFA and screw the reservation system? there are many guild that can camp 30 50+ alts not even primaries in a given area and just rotate at members until they have all they want which could take months per guild.<br>
<br>
Do you poachers think its fun to organize a large group of people who maybe there for the first time and find 30 mobs in 8 hours?<br>
<br>
I thought we were a civilized server I thought we the majority aside from ASURA agreed to abide by the raid calandar?<br>
<br>
I asked that everyone Condemn this sort of behavior and condemn anyone that might condone it in anyway<br>
to the point of blacklisting these people who support and actively participate in FFA that is detrimental to the planes or poaching of the planes.<br>
<br>
Anyhow they have succeeded in one thing, I will not run any more open raids, I am 2.5 for 3 on successful and enjoyable <br>
raids the PoG raid was a very big disappointment for me and for most that attended so I only count it as a half success.<br>
