<br>
You said assuming a 13 hour respawn...most mobs in PoG are on a 24 hour timer plus or minus a bit. Treants i think were a week with the lesser named 3 days. So if raid before you started at say 7pm est and finished 1am est and you started your raid at 2pm est the next day and left at 6pm est, then you were still an hour or so away from mobs respawning. see why a 24 hour reservation onm the calendar is nothing more then luck as to what you will have to kill......<br>
<br>
We stopped scheduling raids to PoG(when SS still went at all) and would just check to see what was up on days no one had it reserved.<br>
